The mobilizer extension is provided by Mixxer, Inc. as a reference for how to
use our API. The Mixxer API is was designed to allow third parties to give
their users the option of making content mobile, or sharing it with friends.

We provide no guarentee that this extension will be bug free, but we hope it
will be useful.

Mixxer is, and will continue to be, free for this type of usage. We sell
premium content to pay the bills, but our main focus is mobile community
applications.

If you would like changes to this extension, have a patch, would like a job or
don't like me please contact mxxr-dev@lists.mixxer.com, we appreciate the
feedback.

Portions of this code were taken from the Adblock plugin and are subject to
that licensing and copyright the appropriate authors.
